{"tid":2008274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人講今日遊行","createTime":"2020-05-09T02:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T02:47:05.000Z","uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8320be29a39dad014ece01ba6d4c0cfdf00d5ed","tid":2008274,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"啲post去哂邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb27c6a87e416cb20b8a914cb9ddeb81e06d049","tid":2008274,"uid":345490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4827426430602cab7b9bc81c467c73d768980c65","tid":2008274,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"【高手過招】政治專家教你打贏輿論戰 同藍絲鬧交成日鬧輸嘅你一定要睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005539</a><br />\n<br />\n35+爭取嚟做咩？35+就係攞嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>罷免港共政府</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n「如果美國要求中國就中共病毒賠償，中國一定會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「如果啲一帶一路投資失敗啲非洲國家要賠償，中國一定都會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GET MY MONEY BACK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要攞返我啲錢<br />\n香港人啲錢唔係比港共亂咁洗</span></span><br />\n香港納稅人財政儲備 不是中共提款機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攞返我啲錢</span></strong></span>」就係我哋對攬炒嘅論述<br />\n「<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果這是攬炒，我們不怕承認</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港財政儲備絕對唔可以比中共當係提款機嚟用<br />\n唔可以攞嚟起啲濕鳩明日大嶼<br />\n唔可以攞嚟找一帶一路啲數 債務<br />\n更加唔可以攞香港啲錢嚟賠償中共病毒索償費用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n高鐵已經有版我哋睇<br />\n高鐵造價853億沒有帶來經濟效益 卻只有贈送中共病毒（武漢肺炎）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-10_NQdC3_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬抄 就是從港共手中搶返屬於我哋嘅血汗錢<br />\n<br />\n立法會35+之後就係要否決預算案<br />\n推冧港共之後再建立一個<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民主主權國家<br />\n35+就是「罷免港共行動」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國係中共病毒疫情之後將會比全球杯葛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聰明嘅香港人要及時止蝕同中國割席<br />\n因為一個獨立主權國家<br />\n係國際舞台先會有競爭力<br />\n先至可以同鄰近嘅星加坡，台灣一較高下</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港只要唔係民主主權國家，人哋係唔撚會show你，亦都唔會有信心返嚟香港投資</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攬炒就是<br />\n「從港共手中搶回屬於香港人金庫」<br />\n「建立民主主權國家  才是爭取國際競爭力的致勝之道」"},{"pid":"8abd3ac9f6b8f218684bf64852c6b6cf1e197882","tid":2008274,"uid":262358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"10號喎唔係咩"},{"pid":"e2d6844831de91adb1b3494d179594116d95eb8e","tid":2008274,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8abd3ac9f6b8f218684bf64852c6b6cf1e197882","tid":2008274,"uid":262358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"10號喎唔係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"係喎 柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}